            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Atilius <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Sp</abbr><ex>uri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Vot</abbr><ex>uria</ex></expan> Pri<lb break="no" n="3"/>mus interrex <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV idem |(centurio) <lb n="5"/>negotiator <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>LXXX <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Atilius Cog<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>ta</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="8"/>tus Atilia <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberta</ex></expan> Fau<lb break="no" n="9"/>sta Privatus et <lb n="10"/>Martialis <expan><abbr>hered</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Kolník: Z. 3: inter(p)rex; AE 1978; AE 1988; Mosser: Z. 3: interprex; Hošek: Z. 3: inter tre{x} (cenarios); AE 1978: Z. 4/5: (centurio) negotiator; Z. 6: LXXX / h(ic); Harl - Lőrincz: Z. 8/9: &amp;lt;F=E&amp;gt;au/sta; Mosser: Z. 7/8: Cocta/tus; Z. 8-10: Fau/sta et Martialis; Z. 11: p(osuerunt).</p>
            </div>
